  <h3>IGF-1 LR3 (Long R3 Insulin-like Growth Factor-1)</h3>
  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Length:</strong> 83 amino acids &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Type:</strong> Synthetic growth factor analog &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Half-Life:</strong> 20&ndash;30 hours &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Parent Compound:</strong> Human IGF-1 (70 amino acids) &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Route:</strong> Subcutaneous injection &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>FDA Status:</strong> Not approved for human use; research chemical only &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Primary Actions:</strong> Anabolic, anti-catabolic, lipolytic, recovery-enhancing</p>
